data.description: SELLERS OFFERING up to $5,000 TOWARDS CLOSING COSTS OR RATE BUY DOWN! Escape to your own piece of paradise in beautiful Trenton, Florida! This spacious 4 bedroom, 3 bathroom home is nestled on a serene one-acre lot, offering the perfect blend of comfort and tranquility. Key Features:   4 Bedrooms: Plenty of room for a growing family or guests.  3 Bathrooms: No more morning rush-hour traffic!  Expansive Yard: 1 acre of lush green space to enjoy.  Open Concept Living: Perfect for entertaining and family gatherings.  Beautifully Remodeled Modern Kitchen: Well-appointed with all the essentials.  Ample Parking: Space for multiple vehicles. Peaceful Location: Experience the joys of country living. Outdoor Bliss: Explore the beautiful outdoors in your own backyard.  Convenient Location: Close to Trenton's amenities and schools.  Just a short drive to Chiefland, Jonesville and Gainesville for shopping, dining and entertainment. This charming home is ready to welcome its new owners with open arms. Whether you're looking for a family retreat or a quiet haven away from the city, this property has it all. Don't miss out on this incredible opportunity! Contact us today to arrange a visit and make this wonderful house your new home.
